The Katsina State Police Command has arrested a 28-year-old terrorist, Suleman Iliyasu, who confessed to have killed no fewer than 15 persons in different banditry operations across the state. The Spokesperson of the Command, SP Gambo Isah, paraded the suspected terrorists also known as “Yar’bushiya” before pressmen at the Command’s headquarter on Tuesday. Yar’bushiya also confessed to have participated in several armed robbery, kidnapping and cattle rustling operations carried out at Dandume, Faskari, Jibia, Batsari, and Kurfi LGA of Katsina State. The criminal promised to turn a new leaf if forgiven. Yar’bushiya, who claimed to be from Walawa Asaurara, Sabuwar Ungwa, Jibia LGA, Katsina State also disclosed that he is a member of Dankarami’s terrorist gang. Dankarami, a notorious terrorist, is wanted by the Police for his involvement in crime against humanity across Nigeria’s north western states.